pylibssh2 (1.0.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * src/channel.c, libssh2/channel.py:
    - Add support for non blocking mode
    - Add read_stderr binding
  * src/session.c, libssh2/session.py:
    - Add support for non blocking mode
    - Add setblocking, getblocking, blockdirections binding
  * examples/ssh_exec2.py:
    - Add example to demonstrate non blocking capabilities.
  * Thanks goes to Morian, cvss and aaloksood

 -- Tristan de Cacqueray <tdc@wallix.com>  Tue, 10 Jul 2012 11:51:42 +0200

pylibssh2 (1.0.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * src/session.c:
    - Add userauth_agent for ssh-agent based authentication

